## Project Summary and Goals

Build an Infrastructure as Code deployment pattern for Azure Virtual Desktop in the True Value Azure tenant.

The immediate goal is to build a disposable Proof of Concept that validates whether Azure Virtual Desktop can meet the needs of the Hexaware contractor teams currently using VMware Horizon. If the PoC is successful, the Bicep modules, deployment patterns, design decisions, and lessons learned from this repository will inform a future production deployment in a separate production subscription.

The primary user groups are:

* Hexaware Operations users
* Hexaware Development users

